Package: pdf2pptx
Title: Renders PDF presentations into PPTX files
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Jiri",
           family = "Lukavsky",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "jiri.lukavsky@ff.cuni.cz",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1082-229X"))
Description: The package extends R Markdown workflow. It allows to renders Beamer presenations into images and creates a PPTX presentation from these images. This allows to present in environments which require PowerPoint files, without compromising rendering quality or introducing potential font/resizing problems.
